Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A brave heart and incredible deductions,\Na rhythm that jumps to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a unique mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A prosperous business leads to a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:47.06,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,The Secret of the High Sales
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.73,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Teitan Primary School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't your family own a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that restaurant! It's the Manpuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's dark and dirty, and the food is disgusting,\Nso the place is always empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why do you think that man is suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because, two months ago, he appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Kamekura Yuuji. I owe a favor\Nto the deceased owner and I'd like to repay him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.81,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Kamekura Yuuji (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To my deceased husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe him something so important\Nthat I can't express it with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, to demonstrate my enormous gratitude,\NI would like to stay here and work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to live with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But we don't have the money to hire another worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking to be paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me stay and work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, he invited himself to live with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think there is something wrong, because my grandfather\Nwho died was selfish and had a bad personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that he never did a favor for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that that man is after something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I want the Detective Boys to discover what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:27.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought it would be an interesting case, but it's only\Na liar that has intruded into someone's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that he is planning a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything about it sounds {\i1}really{\i0} suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! The time has come for the Detective Boys to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would really like to go, but I have other things to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't leave us Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Manpuku restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the restaurant is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look at how many people are waiting to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't had any customers today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there is nobody around, like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, there are a lot of clean restaurants\Nwith delicious food out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I have a lot of experience as a chef,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am going to teach you guys how to cook and redecorate\Nthe shop so that it attracts more customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Redecorate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will pay for all of it, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to repay him for when he helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:05:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, the restaurant has been doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's suspicious about him using his own money to\Nredecorate the restaurant to show his gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's a very grateful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to make the business boom and\Nthen run off with the profit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think that's what he's planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's what he wanted, then why is he helping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be faster to just find a profitable\Nrestaurant in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez... A crime? What a stupid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I am thinking of a new menu. Please\Ndo not disturb. Kamekura."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he has been in his room day and\Nnight creating a new menu for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't let us enter because he says\Nhe wants to keep his menu a secret—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of work to do. Since\Nyou are here, give us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, say goodbye to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the shop has a lot of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the family will spend most of its time working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:14.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}During that time, he's in his room doing something secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This, without a doubt, reminds\Nme of The Red-Headed League!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys, I am sure this is the same as The Red-Headed League.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, The Red-Headed League!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Red-Headed League is one of the 60 famous\Ncases that Sherlock Holmes investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man worked for a store as an employee, and convinced\Nthe owner to leave by finding him another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the owner was working, he dug an underground\Ntunnel to rob the bank next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a grand and very daring crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thanks for the complete explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:03.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However, I would like to add that it was\Nwritten more than 100 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:08.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I doubt that there is a thief nowadays that has the\Npatience to dig a tunnel to steal something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's digging a tunnel, we should be able to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prove it, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Rintaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, sorry to bother you while you're busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you're like a god of good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since you've arrived, the restaurant\Nhas been doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you show me your hands, I'll check your good fortune line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at them however long you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, what did his good fortune line say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't looking at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of blisters and calluses on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're hands that have been using a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe, but he is digging a hole under the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you so, I knew I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko figured it out this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could something like this seriously be happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Anyway, we need to find where he's digging a tunnel to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it now. The nearest bank to the\NManpuku restaurant is on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.99,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been closed for more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be his objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were wrong, it looks like you've failed again, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the place the thief is interested in has to be closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a jewelry store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for our jewelry store to be robbed, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After a previous incident, we installed a\Nsecurity system that can't be breached.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bad experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, a thief stole 3 million yen worth of jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, the thief hasn't been captured yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:42.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A jewel thief, and he hasn't been captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then it is possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us when those jewels were stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well this coming month would make five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jewel thief, and a suspicious man\Ndigging a tunnel underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:07.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey Mitsuhiko, don't tell me you're thinking {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go, I'm very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you ask her, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've solved the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man named Kamekura is, without a doubt, the\Nthief that robbed the jewelry store five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the jewel thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am convinced that my hypothesis is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:41.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I also thought the same thing, but that\Ndeduction has many dark spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this thief is not stupid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he sold all the jewels at once, he would\Nhave been found out and captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was also risky to keep the jewels during\Nall of those years, so he buried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably buried them under Rintaro's house,\Nas it was being reconstructed at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know that the house was being reconstructed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that what you were asking the woman earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamekura came into their house as a worker\Nso that he could dig little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and in this simple way recover all his stolen jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a perfect deduction, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on. It wasn't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing. Even though I thought the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did he wait for five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious that he was waiting until\Nthe five year crime expiration ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, pretty soon he can dig them up and\Nsell them all without a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are correct in that the prosecution\Nfor a criminal case is five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the expiration period of a civil crime is 20 years.\NEven if he gets the jewels now, they won't belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know the laws by heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we didnt know that detail, surely\Nthe thief doesn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just have to argue about everything,\Ndon't you Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother always tells me that sometimes it's better\Nto just accept things without arguing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the police right away and tell them that\Nhe's the jewel thief that they're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have proof. You're going to humiliate yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine, all we have to do is catch him red handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will lay a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A trap? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you guys again. Do you want\Nto see the palm of my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to tell you that we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't easily trick the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now the only thing we have to do is\Nwait for him to fall into our trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what is supposed to happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is going to panic, make a mistake, and we'll discover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:37.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How is it possible for an adult to be scared by\Na threat from a bunch of primary school kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.77,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,The Next Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The whole family is going\Nto a hot spring this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that man recommended to my father that we should go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because we haven't rested a day since\Nthe reopening of the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And of course, that man isn't going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he says only family members should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way he can get everybody to\Nleave, so he can finish digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, Conan! He fell into our trap and is hurrying to dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have the slightest idea of what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like this case is confusing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why would a criminal panic over\Na few words said by some kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable! There are a bunch\Nof things that don't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you are confused because this criminal doesn't do\Nthe same things as the criminals you usually handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a very simple person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm even more confused now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has lost his confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this time he's really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't rebel and become a juvenile delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't like it if that happened to a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I have a friend that lives around here\Nand I already made plans with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What luck! Before we couldn't even\Nafford to have a day of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thanks to Kamekura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the restaurant is doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're lucky that such a good man came to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like everyone just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now to wait for Kamekura to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to wait all night? What if he doesn't show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are we going to tell our parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now all we have to do is get into the restaurant with the\Nkey that Rintaro left us, and catch him red handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been digging for days and still haven't found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have buried them too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found them! The jewels, the jewels, my precious treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We now know that you buried the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we aren't the police, so we can't arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go where? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what else? Aren't you going to\Ntell the criminal your deductions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We left the best part for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you haven't done much this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I have nothing to say to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamekura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, five years ago you entered a jewelry\Nstore and stole three million yen's worth of jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't contradict me, I know what I say is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you just admitted your crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I'm not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that, if I sold them, the police would locate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:18:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I saw that this house was being reconstructed,\Nburied the jewels underground, and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I then worked day after day so the\Npolice wouldn't suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to bear everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such as being screamed at and hit by my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even my friends stopped working as apprentices\Nbecause they couldn't stand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed that, in five years, those jewels would be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what inspired me to keep going,\Nno matter what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, after five years, the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait for the crime expiration date to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dig right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you invented a story to work\Nhere and start digging up the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't easy, since there weren't any customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The family members were always sitting around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no chance for you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you decided to spend your own\Nsavings to renovate this restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and teach them some cooking skills that you've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, making the business prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made it so the entire family was in the\Nrestaurant and kept busy the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, you could start your work\Ndigging and looking for the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Kamekura Yuuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We hit the bulls eye. We're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I don't understand though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you start panicking? Just because some primary\Nschool kids told you that they knew everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm such a coward. I even got scared\Nafter hearing the words "Detective Boys".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for a normal adult to be afraid just because\Na bunch of little kids say a bunch of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just send all of them\Nto the hot spring from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would have been easier, cheaper, and faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you gave them a free trip instead of wasting that money,\Nreforming the restaurant, and waiting for it to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an absurd plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Convinced?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you before that this man was way simpler\Nthan the other criminals you have encountered?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're already here, I called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incredible! Maybe we'll be rewarded by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they will. After all, you guys did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate this. Even after solving the case, I feel horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:52.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We received a letter of thanks for helping in the jewel\Nthief's arrest before the case's expiration period.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so easy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that most criminals aren't as idiotic as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So don't let your guard down because of this.\NIt was dangerous to follow him like we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's wrong with you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NYou have been very jittery lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've felt humiliated since we\Nstole your thunder, right Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Don't you see that\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is sulking cause of what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Conan. It's really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:38.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My intelligence should be used in\Nsolving complex criminal cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:41.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}where our brains engage in a spectacular battle of wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:43.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't really care about these minor cases at all!
